{"tid":363433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷：香港民主運動　新階段　「香港人民運動」","createTime":"2017-08-17T15:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T18:09:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb2a6193e506cc885fdbb4590b6b7550ea4e799","tid":363433,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170815/20121866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170815%2F20121866&d=wf1j%2FBAVpNFcDbTK2ztEXwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1935cc5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170815%2F20121866&h=05fc9270\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170815/20121866</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民主運動到了此刻，必須跳出《基本法》的框框，重新定位，演進為「香港人民運動」。根據國際法，「人民」享有自決的權利，可透過各種方式實現，包括成為主權國內享有民主自治權的自治政府，或民主聯邦國家中的一個地方政府，也可成為獨立的主權國家。重點是「人民」可自主及共同地透過民主程序，決定這群體的政治地位。<br />\n<br />\n港人若能實現自決，必是因中國內部的政治權力平衡出現了重大變化。故香港最終會以甚麼形式實現自決，一方面取決於中國內部出現的重大變化會是甚麼，另一方面也應是由港人自主地決定。香港人民運動在現階段，應包容各個派別，包括民主派、自決派和港獨派。<br />\n<br />\n中國內部的政治權力平衡何時會出現重大變化，沒人能預知。因此，香港人民運動必須準備好長期抗爭，及當未來出現轉變時能及時回應。無論中國內部的政治權力平衡會出現甚麼重大變化，或是中共進行政改、或是中共崩潰瓦解、或是中國陷入四分五裂、或是中國重組成民主聯邦或邦聯。一點不變的，就是港人必須強化「人民意識」，才能在未來日子，堅韌地應對強烈打壓，採取有力行動去繼續增加體制內外及香港內外的政治資本，好在出現重大變化之時，能靈活、及時和有序地自主前路。<br />\n<br />\n只有調整好心態，知道要面對曠日持久的抗爭，我們才不會被眼前一時的困難和迫害所嚇怕或心灰。眼前內部的分歧也不再那麼重要，因前路會有很多變數，故現在大家不用執着於一些想法，因無論是哪看法現階段也難說對錯。這認知會有利於運動的各方結聚力量，去做好長期的部署。有了長遠計劃，我們才不會每次都是被動地在被攻時去守，還可主動地找尋對手的弱點適時發出攻擊。"},{"pid":"00fdd2c220abfb3147bbea1688b8d51edf2f4621","tid":363433,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫香港自決運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15225c9b5271bdb0acc083a11c6636011b51b905","tid":363433,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 豬一般的隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2b75d0983f30160a2f539b007e625ba41d60b4","tid":363433,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"咪又係等支爆"},{"pid":"3db3231a04b4393ca574a3243bd58974f824673a","tid":363433,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔叫香港自決運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前有個研討會　佢話香港要建立自主意識"},{"pid":"8ef15c0d3d7a8f132f9cdc77050e4af6708f1308","tid":363433,"uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"summary=戴耀廷正式搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ed994e8161b81eb37a7517c6a394c91fc0d94e","tid":363433,"uid":100337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"希望佢真係醒覺啦"},{"pid":"7f882bfa73d2f98b86712adf263009b7cef0bf03","tid":363433,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"死開d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec44a399be203cae8a83726a319403afff6a3ea","tid":363433,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔叫香港自決運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「民主」 呢兩個字係年輕人眼中好撚奀耳"},{"pid":"f47c70fab14d41daffa34065e7813ac953fa435e","tid":363433,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望佢真係醒覺啦</blockquote><br />\n戴妖仲有幻想民主中國"},{"pid":"171e30294f2201107ce344ce7007e89ace4d3596","tid":363433,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"831742f49309518831e1a43df8ba920656dd354c","tid":363433,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戴妖真係騎劫本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e82ec1b1aff92944b4839107f8c3b16f5b0fec4","tid":363433,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔叫香港自決運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「民主」 呢兩個字係年輕人眼中好撚奀耳</blockquote><br />\n香港人民運動都好un耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同人民公社差唔多feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}